{"tid":1731350,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"「占卜師」3點前一定要救人！！！","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T13:20:35.000Z","uid":10777,"like":205,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"60380a5960b933b55a77c093dcf9f923200caae8","tid":1731350,"uid":10777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEDXzi2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEDXzi2.png&h=5ae64938&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99Vi3co.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99Vi3co.png&h=ba7181e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，心憂理大手足而卜了一卦，得六爻卦如圖。<br />\n先試試解釋第二張圖。<br />\n當中以世為用神，代表一眾被困手足，暫受子時所生2300-0100，而有一時苟且喘息。<br />\n<br />\n但世位於六爻中第二高位，表示已被步步緊迫，幾乎迫上梁山，形勢非常危急，而且不得日支午火所生，待丑0100-0300時一過，恐怕為時已晚。<br />\n<br />\n特別是代表敵方（死黑警）的應方屬午火，正好受日支所護，得一日之勢，而不是理大手足的一時之勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">待寅時（0300-0500）來到，午寅相合火勢更猛，便時日俱備，將直搗皇龍，手足下場不敢想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span><br />\n<br />\n再看卦象（第一張圖），本卦和變卦為謙卦，此爻謙卑者吉，反之，高傲者凶。如涉水過河，知道危險、人力渺小，則能安然渡過。<span style=\"color: red;\">而高傲者，以暴虎馮河的蠻勇，自以為人力勝天，就會遭至滅頂之災。</span><br />\n<br />\n而最重要的互卦，竟然求得雷水解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，解除、解脫、解放，危難散去，赦免。<br />\n<br />\n解也和「懈」字同義，即懈怠的懈，表示怠慢。《雜卦傳》：「解，緩也。」《序卦傳》：「物不可以終難，故受之以解，解者緩也。」易經中以危險、困難的緩解來定義「解」。<br />\n<br />\n歸藏作荔，可能是劦的假借。劦即協之古字，音與解（謝）相近，<span style=\"color: green;\">同心協力，或者是不停地出力，引申也有努力不懈的意思。<br />\n<br />\n解卦又利西南，往西南方去可以得到貴人幫助，受人幫助與支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n總結封象和六爻生克，即<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>最終結果也就是以同心協力，保持謙卑，知道危險、人力渺小的態度，大家一齊不停地出力的行動而讓手足脫離危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n不過時間必須趕在寅時凌晨3點以前，並把焦點放在西南方，可能暢運到和漆咸道交界，A-core嗰邊？岩岩好和佐敦手足裏應外合，反包圍黑警？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後一定要緊記一點，高傲者必敗，會遭至滅頂之災，香港人，手足們加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n如果有高手覺得解得唔岩，求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"b0ba0402ea596b97f134e23784fd463f34c87f1b","tid":1731350,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:02:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0014c012a8dba45e56ab71fd1f59682117954e","tid":1731350,"uid":155971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:03:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39c8845b99d00cd902ea680c005f92a820ea29b5","tid":1731350,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5a41fd69a7944b0a9b8fd9abf3cc36c5700363","tid":1731350,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bf8132306f50a5c16aa8c6a6b6d706274a0b76","tid":1731350,"uid":2285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:03:20.000Z","msg":"推呀 咩方法都好 一定要救人呀"},{"pid":"3dec76442714834ce51b1638dcb19336c563af71","tid":1731350,"uid":47825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac27e89a9b98949b20be9213b91c0e358fa82df0","tid":1731350,"uid":274023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！"},{"pid":"9c3c4390812410c96b7e8dda315e60f5ae9b1b86","tid":1731350,"uid":227637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e731aa288e308beb63a86ce5268d847131dbd0f","tid":1731350,"uid":170185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"15949ebf5195b811d2df9986ea74ba7527680909","tid":1731350,"uid":10777,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港浸會大學校長錢大康、香港理工大學校長滕錦光、香港城市大學校長郭位、香港科技大學校長史維、香港大學校長張翔，聯合呼籲在理工大學一帶的各方克制，並請學生、校友及其他人士盡快離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n叫呢啲校長去哂A-core 嗰邊，等嗰邊黑警唔敢亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623b5b34e21af9f93ce4d8feb8e84c7b196381f6","tid":1731350,"uid":221707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd96854ff0f0111281c1be58830f95d233a6c9b","tid":1731350,"uid":106798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"想知手足學左幾耐？"},{"pid":"17fc26048b423b7815840087999c09e17f53716d","tid":1731350,"uid":10777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbd96854ff0f0111281c1be58830f95d233a6c9b","tid":1731350,"uid":106798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"想知手足學左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"自學，斷斷續續，解得差唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想出分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733da4bdc885229a07cd37abeb1958fdbd08dc80","tid":1731350,"uid":266980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09596eb28a3dfcf31edcdd00a5e7370789152512","tid":1731350,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"請聯絡仲喺Polyu 嘅手足嘅家人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1730533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1730533</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"faeb3b3d5698225d7f3b568dcac4207e86d685e0","tid":1731350,"uid":338654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"0cb0e54fca5b2469d9c7f45c351d832ae1565fb3","tid":1731